# bes-backup .gitignore
#
# Strategy (see references/self-modifying-agent-backup.md):
#   - Track: intentional state (persona, agent-authored skills, cron, memories, config, custom scripts)
#   - Exclude: secrets, runtime state, vendored bundled-skill categories
#   - Bundled-skill categories use **/-style excludes so individual skills can be
#     re-included later via `!skills/<cat>/<skill>/` + `!skills/<cat>/<skill>/**`
#
# Convention: when customizing a bundled skill, add a re-include block at the END
# of this file. See trailing block for examples (none yet — Bes is freshly born).

# ─── Secrets (NEVER track) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.env
auth.json
*.pem
*.key
*-token
*-credentials
.git-credentials

# ─── Runtime / ephemeral state ──────────────────────────────────────────────
sessions/
logs/
audio_cache/
pairing/
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.lock
*.pid
*.sock

# Hermes-internal noisy state
skills/.curator_state
skills/.usage.json
skills/.hub/
skills/.skills_prompt_snapshot.json
.skills_prompt_snapshot.json

# Vendored Hermes source + node bundle (regenerable from install)
hermes-agent/
node/

# ─── Bundled skill categories (vendored — re-include individual skills as needed) ───
# Use `skills/<cat>/**` rather than `skills/<cat>/` so the directory itself is
# tracked-eligible and re-include patterns below can work.
skills/analytics/**
skills/apple/**
skills/autonomous-ai-agents/**
skills/creative/**
skills/data-science/**
skills/devops/**
skills/dogfood/**
skills/email/**
skills/gaming/**
skills/github/**
skills/mcp/**
skills/media/**
skills/mlops/**
skills/note-taking/**
skills/productivity/**
skills/red-teaming/**
skills/research/**
skills/smart-home/**
skills/social-media/**
skills/software-development/**
skills/yuanbao/**

# ─── Re-include exceptions for customized bundled skills ────────────────────
# When you customize a bundled skill, add lines like:
#   !skills/productivity/linear/
#   !skills/productivity/linear/SKILL.md
# (none yet — Bes is fresh)

# Agent-authored skill: work-log (vault daily-note work-log generator)
!skills/note-taking/work-log/
!skills/note-taking/work-log/**

# Tracked customizations of bundled skill: obsidian
# (vault path, vault conventions, OFM reference)
!skills/note-taking/obsidian/
!skills/note-taking/obsidian/SKILL.md
!skills/note-taking/obsidian/references/
!skills/note-taking/obsidian/references/**

# Tracked customizations of bundled skill: google-workspace
# (scopes patched to read-only; SKILL.md banner explaining the constraint)
!skills/productivity/google-workspace/
!skills/productivity/google-workspace/SKILL.md
!skills/productivity/google-workspace/scripts/
!skills/productivity/google-workspace/scripts/setup.py

# Broader allowlist for google-workspace scripts (gws_multi.py, etc.)
!skills/productivity/google-workspace/scripts/**
# But never commit __pycache__ from within the allowlisted scripts dir
skills/productivity/google-workspace/scripts/__pycache__/

# Agent-authored skill: bes-email-dispatch (handler for forwarded-email workflow)
!skills/note-taking/bes-email-dispatch/
!skills/note-taking/bes-email-dispatch/**
# Exclude pycache from within the allowlisted dir
skills/note-taking/bes-email-dispatch/**/__pycache__/
skills/note-taking/bes-email-dispatch/**/*.pyc

# Agent-authored skill: slack (SignLab workspace, user-token via xoxp-)
!skills/social-media/slack/
!skills/social-media/slack/**
# Exclude pycache from within the allowlisted dir
skills/social-media/slack/**/__pycache__/
skills/social-media/slack/**/*.pyc

# Tracked customizations of bundled skills: jq-pipe migration (replaced
# `| python3 -m json.tool` with `| jq .` so Hermes tirith scanner stops
# flagging curl|interpreter as HIGH risk on every API call). Full-dir
# allowlist so future patches/refs/scripts get backed up automatically.
!skills/productivity/linear/
!skills/productivity/linear/**
!skills/productivity/airtable/
!skills/productivity/airtable/**
# Exclude pycache from any of the above
skills/productivity/linear/**/__pycache__/
skills/productivity/airtable/**/__pycache__/

# Agent-authored skill: todoist (Doist MCP server wrapper — task management for Hermes + Bes)
!skills/productivity/todoist/
!skills/productivity/todoist/**
# Exclude pycache from within the allowlisted dir
skills/productivity/todoist/**/__pycache__/
skills/productivity/todoist/**/*.pyc

# Custom skill — task-inbox-fill (Bes-only)
!skills/productivity/task-inbox-fill/
!skills/productivity/task-inbox-fill/**
skills/productivity/task-inbox-fill/**/__pycache__/
skills/productivity/task-inbox-fill/**/*.pyc

# Agent-authored skill: obsidian-manage-categories (Bes manages vault category notes/templates)
!skills/note-taking/
!skills/note-taking/obsidian-manage-categories/
!skills/note-taking/obsidian-manage-categories/**

# Agent-authored skill: obsidian-people-notes (Bes creates People/Org vault notes)
!skills/note-taking/obsidian-people-notes/
!skills/note-taking/obsidian-people-notes/**

# Agent-authored skill: did-i-already-do-this (Bes looks up whether Justin already did something)
!skills/note-taking/did-i-already-do-this/
!skills/note-taking/did-i-already-do-this/**

# Agent-authored skill: llm-wiki (compounding vault knowledge / Inputs-Sources integration)
!skills/note-taking/llm-wiki/
!skills/note-taking/llm-wiki/**

# Tracked customization: obsidian-hygiene (vault hygiene operator docs)
!skills/note-taking/obsidian-hygiene/
!skills/note-taking/obsidian-hygiene/**

# Agent-authored skill: manage-projects (cross-tool project workflow — Todoist sub-project + Obsidian note)
!skills/productivity/manage-projects/
!skills/productivity/manage-projects/**

# Exclude pycache from the four agent-authored skills above
skills/note-taking/obsidian-manage-categories/**/__pycache__/
skills/note-taking/obsidian-people-notes/**/__pycache__/
skills/note-taking/did-i-already-do-this/**/__pycache__/
skills/note-taking/llm-wiki/**/__pycache__/
skills/note-taking/obsidian-hygiene/**/__pycache__/
skills/productivity/manage-projects/**/__pycache__/

# Tracked customization of bundled skill: apple/imessage
# Scoped read-only via SSH proxy to host (allowlist of 13 chats).
# Only SKILL.md is patched — references/ stays upstream (none currently).
!skills/apple/imessage/
!skills/apple/imessage/SKILL.md

# Custom skill: software-development/bes-skill-authoring
# Only SKILL.md is patched — no references/scripts customized.
!skills/software-development/
!skills/software-development/bes-skill-authoring/
!skills/software-development/bes-skill-authoring/SKILL.md
